WEBVTT

00:00.421 --> 00:04.059
You are Mr White's child
and you're to be married, are you not?

00:04.179 --> 00:05.878
Not as at 3 o'clock this afternoon.

00:05.998 --> 00:08.122
Why must it be the daughters who suffer?

00:08.243 --> 00:09.787
What you told me...

00:10.096 --> 00:12.360
***

00:12.480 --> 00:13.908
No brown, either.

00:14.028 --> 00:15.882
He was right on both counts.

00:16.190 --> 00:18.221
***

00:18.341 --> 00:21.607
**

00:21.727 --> 00:23.194
***

00:23.484 --> 00:26.870
***

00:26.990 --> 00:29.463
