00:32.718 --> 00:36.283
***

00:36.403 --> 00:39.841
***

00:40.498 --> 00:41.414
Okay?

00:41.649 --> 00:43.845
It wasn't my son who died here.

00:43.965 --> 00:45.163
It was an innocent boy.

00:45.391 --> 00:46.758
His name was Roger.

00:47.127 --> 00:48.107
You get that?

00:48.464 --> 00:49.267
I did.

00:49.387 --> 00:51.411
I am with the Pinkerton Detective Agency.

00:51.531 --> 00:54.479
These men are my associates and witness to your confession to

00:54.599 --> 00:55.969
First degree murder.

00:56.598 --> 00:57.997
I know you like to relax.

00:58.051 --> 01:00.784
I've been meaning to talk to you
about expanding my role in your gang.

01:00.823 --> 01:02.993
You wouldn't squeeze me
out of my own operation...

01:03.003 --> 01:03.600
Get down!

01:06.650 --> 01:07.839
Lucky for Johnny,

01:07.959 --> 01:09.486
he left when he did, huh?

01:10.336 --> 01:12.416
What's on your mind?

01:12.536 --> 01:13.927
I want out!

